        public JSONObject toJSON()

        Gets a JSONObject containing the values of TAG_KEY and POST_KEY as currently configured.

        Returns:
        A JSONObject containing the values of TAG_KEY and POST_KEY as currently configured, or null if one or both of those values have not yet been set.

      • fromJSON

        public static ServerRequest fromJSON(JSONObject json)

        Converts a JSONObject object containing keys stored as key-value pairs into a ServerRequest.

        Parameters:
        json - A JSONObject object containing post data stored as key-value pairs
        Returns:
        A ServerRequest object with the POST_KEY and TAG_KEY values set if not null; this can be one or the other. If both values in the supplied JSONObject are null, null is returned instead of an object.
